OL,3,C'Self preservation' stopping victims
OL,4,Cfrom getting answers, disaster expert
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"It is very, very hard to come to
OL,8,Fterms with. To constantly see self-
OL,9,Fpreservation, denial, othering of the
OL,10,Fvictim, and just a massive effort -
OL,11,Feffort that could have been put in to
OL,12,Fpreventing an incident - put into
OL,13,Fconspiring."
OL,15,FProf Easthope spoke to Granada as
OL,16,FManchester marks seven years since a
OL,17,Fleft 22 dead and hundreds injured.
OL,19,FProf Easthope grew up in Liverpool and
OL,20,Fwas inspired into a career in public
OL,21,Fsafety following the events at in 1989.
