OL,3,C'Self preservation' stopping victims
OL,4,Cfrom getting answers, disaster expert
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FShe said: "I know that the families
OL,8,Fand those affected by all of these
OL,9,Fincidents, and I know that the public
OL,10,Fwant me to say 'yes, enough is being
OL,11,Fdone', but the answer is no, not
OL,12,Fnearly enough is being done," she told
OL,13,FLucy Meacock.
OL,15,F"Several of the major recommendations
OL,16,Fof the are still not not there yet."
OL,18,FProf Easthope also called for more
OL,19,Ftrust to be given to local communities
OL,20,Fwho feel like injustice has been
OL,21,Fcarried out.
