OL,7,FProf Easthope is a Professor in
OL,8,FPractice of Risk and Hazard at the
OL,9,FUniversity of Durham and Fellow in
OL,10,FMass Fatalities and Pandemics at the
OL,11,FCentre for Death and Society,
OL,12,FUniversity of Bath.
OL,14,FWhile she has seen evidence which
OL,15,Fsuggests state agencies do work
OL,16,Ftogether better in the aftermath of a
OL,17,Fterror incident, she has also seen
OL,18,Fincident commanders "struggling to
OL,19,Fbelieve they'll be in the hot seat"
OL,20,Fand in some cases "struggling with
OL,21,Fdeclaring a major incident".
