OL,3,C'Self preservation' stopping victims
OL,4,Cfrom getting answers, disaster expert
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"We went into the early 2000s with
OL,8,Fagencies particularly police and fire
OL,9,Fand ambulance not working terribly
OL,10,Fwell together," she said.
OL,12,F"We've worked so hard to fix that. We
OL,13,Fhave seen venue improvement. We have
OL,14,Fseen security improvement.
OL,16,F"Where we've stalled is around things
OL,17,Flike first aid and public awareness."
