OL,3,C'Self preservation' stopping victims
OL,4,Cfrom getting answers, disaster expert
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FMaking the public aware of what they
OL,8,Fcan do in the aftermath of an
OL,9,Fincident; how they can assist the
OL,10,Femergency services and even provide
OL,11,Ffirst aid are among the measures which
OL,12,Fcould help Britain respond better, the
OL,13,Fprofessor said.
OL,15,F"So we aren't having true honest
OL,16,Fconversations about what it takes to
OL,17,Flead in these sort of incidents, and
OL,18,Fwhat resources are needed to prepare
OL,19,Fus," she added.
